[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":406},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fother\u002F20211204\u002F2579354992\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fother\u002F20211204\u002F2579354992\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fother\u002F20211204\u002F2579354992\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fother\u002F20211204\u002F2579354992\u002F":381,"related:\u002Fother\u002F20211204\u002F2579354992\u002F":390},"\u002Fen\u002Fmisc\u002F2021\u002F12\u002F04\u002Fuseful-browser-extensions-for-developers\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":363,"date":364,"description":18,"extension":365,"lang":366,"meta":367,"navigation":368,"path":369,"readingMinutes":370,"seo":371,"standalone":372,"stem":373,"tags":374,"tldr":378,"updated":378,"url":379,"__hash__":380},"content\u002F雜談\u002F究竟有哪些實用的擴充外掛-Browser-extension？.md","究竟有哪些實用的擴充外掛(Browser extension)？","2579354992",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":348},"minimark",[11,15,19,22,33,39,42,48,51,88,91,98,105,108,111,117,123,129,132,135,141,147,150,156,159,162,168,174,180,183,186,192,198,201,207,213,219,222,226,229,235,241,247,251,254,260,266,272,276,279,284,290,296,300,303,309,315,321,325,328,333,339,345],[12,13,14],"h2",{"id":14},"前言",[16,17,18],"p",{},"瀏覽器的擴充套件類型非常的多，那麼對於一名工程師來講又有哪些實用的擴充套件呢？所以這一篇就介紹一下我本身有安裝的擴充套件有哪些，那麼由於我主要使用 Firefox 瀏覽器，但我也會盡可能同步提供 Chrome 的擴充套件連結。",[12,20,21],{"id":21},"翻譯套件",[16,23,24,25,32],{},"Chrome 瀏覽器的使用者大多都會被推薦使用 ",[26,27,31],"a",{"href":28,"rel":29},"https:\u002F\u002Fchrome.google.com\u002Fwebstore\u002Fdetail\u002Fgoogle-translate\u002Faapbdbdomjkkjkaonfhkkikfgjllcleb?hl=zh-TW",[30],"nofollow","Google 翻譯","，畢竟是自家 Google 開發",[16,34,35],{},[36,37],"img",{"alt":31,"src":38},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002Fb74kRwy.png",[16,40,41],{},"但是我個人推薦使用「沙拉查詞-多字典滑鼠選字翻譯」這個套件",[16,43,44],{},[36,45],{"alt":46,"src":47},"沙拉查詞-多字典滑鼠選字翻譯","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002F1HOMoK7.png",[16,49,50],{},"主要原因在於它支援大量的翻譯字典，例如：",[52,53,54,58,61,64,67,70,73,76,79,82,85],"ul",{},[55,56,57],"li",{},"必應詞典",[55,59,60],{},"美國傳統詞典",[55,62,63],{},"牛津高階詞典",[55,65,66],{},"彩雲小譯",[55,68,69],{},"劍橋詞典",[55,71,72],{},"CNKI翻譯助手",[55,74,75],{},"柯林斯高階",[55,77,78],{},"Etymonline",[55,80,81],{},"雙語例句",[55,83,84],{},"谷歌翻譯",[55,86,87],{},"谷歌詞典",[16,89,90],{},"等等，非常多。",[16,92,93],{},[26,94,97],{"href":95,"rel":96},"https:\u002F\u002Fchrome.google.com\u002Fwebstore\u002Fdetail\u002F%E6%B2%99%E6%8B%89%E6%9F%A5%E8%AF%8D-%E8%81%9A%E5%90%88%E8%AF%8D%E5%85%B8%E5%88%92%E8%AF%8D%E7%BF%BB%E8%AF%91\u002Fcdonnmffkdaoajfknoeeecmchibpmkmg?hl=zh-TW",[30],"Chrome 下載",[16,99,100],{},[26,101,104],{"href":102,"rel":103},"https:\u002F\u002Faddons.mozilla.org\u002Fzh-TW\u002Ffirefox\u002Faddon\u002Fext-saladict",[30],"Firefox 下載",[12,106,107],{"id":107},"色碼查詢",[16,109,110],{},"ColorZilla 是一套色碼查詢套件",[16,112,113],{},[36,114],{"alt":115,"src":116},"ColorZilla","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FoGPnh4X.png",[16,118,119],{},[26,120,97],{"href":121,"rel":122},"https:\u002F\u002Fchrome.google.com\u002Fwebstore\u002Fdetail\u002Fcolorzilla\u002Fbhlhnicpbhignbdhedgjhgdocnmhomnp?hl=zh-TW",[30],[16,124,125],{},[26,126,104],{"href":127,"rel":128},"https:\u002F\u002Faddons.mozilla.org\u002Fzh-TW\u002Ffirefox\u002Faddon\u002Fcolorzilla\u002F",[30],[12,130,131],{"id":131},"顯示網頁伺服器位置",[16,133,134],{},"Flagfox 是一套非常簡單的功能，它會直接顯示你當前瀏覽的網頁頁面伺服器在哪個國家，並依據該國家的國旗顯示在畫面上",[16,136,137],{},[36,138],{"alt":139,"src":140},"Flagfox","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FMOFAKay.png",[16,142,143],{},[26,144,104],{"href":145,"rel":146},"https:\u002F\u002Faddons.mozilla.org\u002Fzh-TW\u002Ffirefox\u002Faddon\u002Fflagfox\u002F",[30],[16,148,149],{},"但是 Chrome 並沒有這個套件，可以你可以改下載另一套「IP Domain Country Flag」也是具有相同功能",[16,151,152],{},[26,153,97],{"href":154,"rel":155},"https:\u002F\u002Fchrome.google.com\u002Fwebstore\u002Fdetail\u002Fip-whois-flags-chrome-web\u002Fkmdfbacgombndnllogoijhnggalgmkon\u002Frelated?hl=zh-TW",[30],[12,157,158],{"id":158},"顯示網頁的字體",[16,160,161],{},"如果你想要查詢某個網頁上的字體叫什麼的話，我個人推薦使用「Fonts Ninja」",[16,163,164],{},[36,165],{"alt":166,"src":167},"Fonts Ninja","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FVkzi2QM.png",[16,169,170],{},[26,171,104],{"href":172,"rel":173},"https:\u002F\u002Faddons.mozilla.org\u002Fzh-TW\u002Ffirefox\u002Faddon\u002Ffonts-ninja\u002F",[30],[16,175,176],{},[26,177,97],{"href":178,"rel":179},"https:\u002F\u002Fchrome.google.com\u002Fwebstore\u002Fdetail\u002Ffonts-ninja\u002Feljapbgkmlngdpckoiiibecpemleclhh?hl=zh-TW",[30],[12,181,182],{"id":182},"查詢網頁使用技術",[16,184,185],{},"Wappalyzer 相信是非常多人裝的套件，但不免也是推薦給各位",[16,187,188],{},[26,189,97],{"href":190,"rel":191},"https:\u002F\u002Fchrome.google.com\u002Fwebstore\u002Fdetail\u002Fwappalyzer\u002Fgppongmhjkpfnbhagpmjfkannfbllamg?hl=zh-TW",[30],[16,193,194],{},[26,195,104],{"href":196,"rel":197},"https:\u002F\u002Faddons.mozilla.org\u002Fzh-TW\u002Ffirefox\u002Faddon\u002Fwappalyzer\u002F",[30],[16,199,200],{},"而另一套我還有額外使用「whatruns」",[16,202,203],{},[36,204],{"alt":205,"src":206},"whatruns","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FHQ3c5JW.png",[16,208,209],{},[26,210,97],{"href":211,"rel":212},"https:\u002F\u002Fchrome.google.com\u002Fwebstore\u002Fdetail\u002Fwhatruns\u002Fcmkdbmfndkfgebldhnkbfhlneefdaaip?hl=zh-TW",[30],[16,214,215],{},[26,216,104],{"href":217,"rel":218},"https:\u002F\u002Faddons.mozilla.org\u002Fzh-TW\u002Ffirefox\u002Faddon\u002Fwhatruns\u002F",[30],[16,220,221],{},"如果論精準度的話，我個人認為 Wappalyzer 是比較精準的。",[12,223,225],{"id":224},"查詢用什麼-cms","查詢用什麼 CMS",[16,227,228],{},"有時候看到某些部落格或者是網站，你可以使用「What CMS Is This」來查詢",[16,230,231],{},[36,232],{"alt":233,"src":234},"What CMS Is This","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FquFq3eO.png",[16,236,237],{},[26,238,97],{"href":239,"rel":240},"https:\u002F\u002Fchrome.google.com\u002Fwebstore\u002Fdetail\u002Fwhat-cms-is-this\u002Fgamohlpmdjkdjepgdgjohkbfpmeelmem?hl=zh-TW",[30],[16,242,243],{},[26,244,104],{"href":245,"rel":246},"https:\u002F\u002Faddons.mozilla.org\u002Fzh-TW\u002Ffirefox\u002Faddon\u002Fwhat-cms-is-this",[30],[12,248,250],{"id":249},"gmail-通知","Gmail 通知",[16,252,253],{},"「Notifier for Gmail」是一套我非常喜歡的擴充套件，這個套件它會通知你有新的信件進來，可以避免你漏信",[16,255,256],{},[36,257],{"alt":258,"src":259},"Notifier for Gmail","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FevpSVDF.png",[16,261,262],{},[26,263,97],{"href":264,"rel":265},"https:\u002F\u002Fchrome.google.com\u002Fwebstore\u002Fdetail\u002Fnotifier-for-gmail\u002Fdcjichoefijpinlfnjghokpkojhlhkgl?hl=zh-TW",[30],[16,267,268],{},[26,269,104],{"href":270,"rel":271},"https:\u002F\u002Faddons.mozilla.org\u002Fen-US\u002Ffirefox\u002Faddon\u002Fgmail-notifier-restartless\u002F",[30],[12,273,275],{"id":274},"查看-json-檔案","查看 JSON 檔案",[16,277,278],{},"如果你是前端工程師，那麼這個套件就不用我在說明了吧。",[16,280,281],{},[36,282],{"alt":275,"src":283},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002F4CFjkxZ.png",[16,285,286],{},[26,287,97],{"href":288,"rel":289},"https:\u002F\u002Fchrome.google.com\u002Fwebstore\u002Fdetail\u002Fjson-viewer\u002Fgbmdgpbipfallnflgajpaliibnhdgobh?hl=zh-TW",[30],[16,291,292],{},[26,293,104],{"href":294,"rel":295},"https:\u002F\u002Faddons.mozilla.org\u002Fzh-TW\u002Ffirefox\u002Faddon\u002Fjsonview",[30],[12,297,299],{"id":298},"seo-分析工具","SEO 分析工具",[16,301,302],{},"這類型的套件就很多了，我主要是使用「SEO Site Tools, Site Analysis」來做分析",[16,304,305],{},[36,306],{"alt":307,"src":308},"SEO Site Tools, Site Analysis","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FLiilA1i.png",[16,310,311],{},[26,312,97],{"href":313,"rel":314},"https:\u002F\u002Fchrome.google.com\u002Fwebstore\u002Fdetail\u002Fseo-site-tools-site-analy\u002Ffemogmcmjpjkokoojcljkpfdifkpbbpp?hl=zh-TW",[30],[16,316,317],{},[26,318,104],{"href":319,"rel":320},"https:\u002F\u002Faddons.mozilla.org\u002Fzh-TW\u002Ffirefox\u002Faddon\u002Fseo-site-tools-site-analysis",[30],[12,322,324],{"id":323},"顯示-html-階層","顯示 HTML 階層",[16,326,327],{},"這個套件可以快速幫你顯示出該頁面上的 HTML 所有階層，也可以用來看出自己在 HTML 規劃上是否得宜",[16,329,330],{},[36,331],{"alt":324,"src":332},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FYPYExAY.png",[16,334,335],{},[26,336,97],{"href":337,"rel":338},"https:\u002F\u002Fchrome.google.com\u002Fwebstore\u002Fdetail\u002Fhtml5-outliner\u002Fafoibpobokebhgfnknfndkgemglggomo",[30],[16,340,341],{},[26,342,104],{"href":343,"rel":344},"https:\u002F\u002Faddons.mozilla.org\u002Fzh-TW\u002Ffirefox\u002Faddon\u002Foutline-sidebar",[30],[16,346,347],{},"那麼以上大概就是我常用的瀏覽器擴充套件囉~",{"title":349,"searchDepth":350,"depth":350,"links":351},"",2,[352,353,354,355,356,357,358,359,360,361,362],{"id":14,"depth":350,"text":14},{"id":21,"depth":350,"text":21},{"id":107,"depth":350,"text":107},{"id":131,"depth":350,"text":131},{"id":158,"depth":350,"text":158},{"id":182,"depth":350,"text":182},{"id":224,"depth":350,"text":225},{"id":249,"depth":350,"text":250},{"id":274,"depth":350,"text":275},{"id":298,"depth":350,"text":299},{"id":323,"depth":350,"text":324},"雜談","2021-12-04 21:49:43","md","zh-Hant",{},true,"\u002Fbrowser-extension","2",{"title":6,"description":18},false,"雜談\u002F究竟有哪些實用的擴充外掛-Browser-extension？",[375,376,377],"Browser extension","Chrome extension","Firefox extension",null,"\u002Fother\u002F20211204\u002F2579354992\u002F","ZmgaPI8LZIlDDF8kH9Ahgv3HFcN9QJViCRMHByFP6js",{"newer":382,"older":386},{"url":383,"title":384,"date":385},"\u002Fnuxt\u002F20211205\u002F3240380460\u002F","Nuxt.js 2.x 實戰手冊(5) - 生命週期(lifecycle)","2021-12-05 15:18:00",{"url":387,"title":388,"date":389},"\u002Fjavascript\u002F20211128\u002F2950137358\u002F","JavaScript 中的 Promise 是什麼？以及為什麼你要懂 Promise","2021-11-28 16:19:37",[391,396,401],{"url":392,"title":393,"date":394,"readingMinutes":395},"\u002Fother\u002F20260710\u002F2193411838\u002F","關於我做了百日挑戰「增肌減脂」這個有趣的實驗","2026-07-10 09:53:56","16",{"url":397,"title":398,"date":399,"readingMinutes":400},"\u002Fother\u002F20260623\u002F2826413095\u002F","Mac 系統監控工具就推薦用 Stats！一款免費又開源，還能看 CPU、GPU、溫度、網速的軟體","2026-06-23 10:00:00","4",{"url":402,"title":403,"date":404,"readingMinutes":405},"\u002Fother\u002F20260526\u002F2846301957\u002F","寫部落格能月入幾萬美金嗎？聊聊 Google AdSense 真實收益與計算方式","2026-05-26 21:00:00","5",1784013092190]